Exploring Weather Patterns in March

Whats going on with this data?

This line plot shows how temperature changed throughout the observation period. The overall trend reveals how temperature fluctuates over different times of the day.

How often was each type of weather observed?

This bar chart displays the number of observations for each weather condition. Clearly, some weather types like sunny or cloudy were more common than others.

Temperature and humidity throughout the day

This scatter plot compares the average temperature and humidity across different times of the day, as well as whether it was a weekday or weekend.

We can see distinct clusters: for example, mornings tend to be cooler and more humid, while afternoons show higher temperatures with lower humidityespecially on weekdays.
